<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Vervium CloudAI</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --paper: #f4f1e9;
      --ink: #1f2a37;
      --accent: #005f73;
      --signal: #ee9b00;
      --card: #fffef9;
      --line: #d5cbb9;
      --muted: #606f7b;
    }

    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: "Trebuchet MS", "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
      color: var(--ink);
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 10% 0%, #fff7d8 0, transparent 38%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 100% 0%, #d9eef2 0, transparent 34%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, #f8f5ed 0%, #efe7d9 100%);
      min-height: 100vh;
    }

    .page {
      max-width: 1040px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 24px;
    }

    .nav {
      border: 2px solid var(--line);
      background: var(--card);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 14px 18px;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .brand {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .brand-badge {
      width: 28px;
      height: 28px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), #0a9396);
      color: #fff;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      font-size: 14px;
      box-shadow: 0 3px 0 #003845;
    }

    .brand small {
      display: block;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 11px;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
    }

    .nav-right {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 14px;
    }

    .nav-right a {
      color: var(--muted);
      text-decoration: none;
      border-bottom: 1px dotted var(--muted);
    }

    .hero {
      margin-top: 26px;
      border: 2px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 16px;
      background: var(--card);
      overflow: hidden;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 1fr;
    }

    .hero-main {
      padding: 34px;
    }

    .kicker {
      display: inline-block;
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      background: #fff3c4;
      border: 1px solid #f0d275;
      border-radius: 999px;
      padding: 6px 12px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    h1 {
      margin: 14px 0 12px;
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.2rem);
      line-height: 1.04;
      letter-spacing: -1px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .hero p {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      line-height: 1.45;
      max-width: 36ch;
    }

    .cta {
      margin-top: 22px;
      display: flex;
      gap: 12px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .btn {
      border: 0;
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 11px 16px;
      font-weight: 800;
      cursor: pointer;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.6px;
    }

    .btn-primary {
      color: white;
      background: var(--accent);
      box-shadow: 0 4px 0 #023a45;
    }

    .btn-secondary {
      color: var(--ink);
      background: #f5f2ea;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
    }

    .hero-side {
      padding: 26px;
      background:
        repeating-linear-gradient(-45deg, #fff7e6, #fff7e6 16px, #fff1d2 16px, #fff1d2 32px);
      border-left: 2px solid var(--line);
      display: grid;
      align-content: center;
      gap: 14px;
    }

    .metric {
      background: #fff;
      border: 1px solid #eadfca;
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 0 #d3c6ae;
    }

    .metric h3 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 12px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .metric strong {
      font-size: 1.4rem;
      display: block;
      margin-top: 4px;
    }

    .grid {
      margin-top: 24px;
      display: grid;
      gap: 16px;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    }

    .card {
      border: 2px solid var(--line);
      background: var(--card);
      border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 18px;
    }

    .card h2 {
      margin: 0 0 8px;
      font-size: 1rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    }

    .card p {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.45;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    .badge {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 12px;
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: #532f00;
      background: #ffd788;
      border: 1px solid #e8b85a;
      border-radius: 999px;
      padding: 5px 9px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .footer {
      margin-top: 20px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: var(--muted);
      text-align: center;
      padding-bottom: 12px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 860px) {
      .hero {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .hero-side {
        border-left: 0;
        border-top: 2px solid var(--line);
      }

      .grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <main class="page">
    <nav class="nav">
      <div class="brand">
        <span class="brand-badge">BC</span>
        <div>
          CloudAI
          <small>by Vervium (Est. 1970)</small>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="nav-right">
        <span>Enterprise-ready since last quarter</span>
      </div>
    </nav>

    <section class="hero">
      <div class="hero-main">
        <span class="kicker">Now with 400% more cloud</span>
        <h1>Legacy Wisdom.<br>AI Speed.</h1>
        <p>
          Vervium proudly brings decades of meeting-heavy excellence into modern SaaS.
          CloudAI automates your workflows, dashboards your dashboards, and puts every deployment
          behind at least three approvals.
        </p>
        <div class="cta">
          <button class="btn btn-primary">Book A Demo</button>
          <button class="btn btn-secondary">Download Whitepaper v12</button>
        </div>
      </div>
      <aside class="hero-side">
        <div class="metric">
          <h3>Quarterly AI Synergy</h3>
          <strong>97.3%</strong>
        </div>
        <div class="metric">
          <h3>Mean Time To PowerPoint</h3>
          <strong>4 min</strong>
        </div>
        <div class="metric">
          <h3>Cloud Adoption Maturity</h3>
          <strong>Bronze+</strong>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </section>

    <section class="grid">
      <article class="card">
        <h2>DevOps Control Tower</h2>
        <p>
          Monitor CI/CD pipelines with executive-friendly gauges that turn yellow before anything is actually wrong.
        </p>
        <span class="badge">ISO-ish Compliant</span>
      </article>
      <article class="card">
        <h2>AI Ticket Summarizer</h2>
        <p>
          Converts 87-comment incident threads into one sentence and three action items no one agreed on.
        </p>
        <span class="badge">Powered by committee</span>
      </article>
      <article class="card">
        <h2>Cost Optimization Engine</h2>
        <p>
          Recommends rightsizing after every outage retrospective, then opens a follow-up task for next fiscal year.
        </p>
        <span class="badge">FinOps-ready</span>
      </article>
    </section>

    <p class="footer">
      Hello, World! Vervium training environment for DevOps classes only.
    </p>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
